_sText:
Original map by Paramedic911

Ported to CS:S by Marfugga. Added a few ladders.
Also added some more barrels, since on my server
you can grab/throw them and this is fun.

NOTE: There are no vehicles in the map by default
because vehicles are unsupported in maps in CSS.
If you want vehicles, play on this 24/7 Jeepathon
server: wew.css44.com:27015

INSTRUCTIONS
-------------
Copy the contents to your 
steamapps/counter-strike:source/cstrike/maps folder!
